1271
01:42:04,377 --> 01:42:06,417
<i>I regretted it to death.</i>

1272
01:42:07,547 --> 01:42:10,797
<i>But I didn't want to stop.</i>

1273
01:42:12,637 --> 01:42:16,847
<i>Your words have
saved me all this time.</i>

1274
01:42:21,477 --> 01:42:22,687
<i>Thank you.</i>

1275
01:42:36,407 --> 01:42:37,957
Welcome back.

1276
01:43:46,767 --> 01:43:50,357
I like you, Kuroda.

1277
01:43:53,567 --> 01:43:57,947
So don't try to end it with a letter.

1278
01:43:59,287 --> 01:44:00,827
Let me hear it clearly.

1279
01:44:02,367 --> 01:44:04,127
I want to hear it clearly.

1280
01:44:08,297 --> 01:44:09,587
Oh, uh...

1281
01:44:19,847 --> 01:44:21,767
Oh!

1282
01:44:24,117 --> 01:44:25,437
What the heck was that?

1283
01:44:26,187 --> 01:44:27,517
Motivation!

1284
01:44:29,527 --> 01:44:33,447
I don't... want to lie
about how I feel anymore.

1285
01:44:38,827 --> 01:44:40,157
I...

1286
01:44:42,827 --> 01:44:45,037
like you, Setoyama!

1287
01:44:47,877 --> 01:44:49,547
I love you!

