1302
01:49:10,177 --> 01:49:12,828
<i>Next, we have a letter
who goes by the radio</i>

1303
01:49:12,840 --> 01:49:15,267
<i>name of "Ms. Lovesick
High School Girl."</i>

1304
01:49:15,387 --> 01:49:18,647
<i>"Compared to my friends,
I lack confidence in myself."</i>

1305
01:49:18,767 --> 01:49:20,567
<i>"I really hate myself
being like that."</i>

1306
01:49:21,777 --> 01:49:26,447
Well, I've been there myself,
so I understand how you feel.

1307
01:49:28,277 --> 01:49:33,537
For example, why don't you try putting
into words what you're thinking right now?

1308
01:49:33,867 --> 01:49:39,377
Write down what you like,
what's troubling you, in a notebook,

1309
01:49:39,667 --> 01:49:41,837
and those words
will give you strength.

1310
01:49:42,757 --> 01:49:44,167
What's important...

1311
01:49:45,047 --> 01:49:47,927
is that you don't lie about how you feel.

1312
01:49:48,967 --> 01:49:50,387
I'm rooting for you!

1313
01:50:03,607 --> 01:50:05,557
- Sorry for the wait!
- Good work.

1314
01:50:06,737 --> 01:50:08,107
- Over there?
- Yeah.

1315
01:50:08,857 --> 01:50:12,197
- You're out early.
- Yeah, I got it done early.

1316
01:50:12,737 --> 01:50:16,367
Have you thought about your speech
for Yoneda and Yuko's wedding?

1317
01:50:16,497 --> 01:50:17,407
Not yet.

1318
